  m_Name: Level 4 Chat
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  messageContentList:
  - message: 'May I have your attention once again? There has been an update to our
      software that I need to alert you of. '
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "It has come to our attention that there are three students in the current
      season of applicants who have been appointed with the <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>\u201CLegendary\u201D</b></wave>
      status. "
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: 'These students are prodigies in their respective fields, and would
      be a great boon to our academy. However, we are unsure of their exact identities.
      All we have for clues are three riddles that point to their identifying features. '
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Click the <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>Legendary Student icon</b></wave> here
      to view them.
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8e4e73ad788d17e4ca0d217fb71f96ca, type: 3}
  - message: 'Using this identifying information, look closely at each student and
      try to sleuth out who the Legendary students might be. If you feel like you
      have a solid suspicion, you may scan the student you have selected with the
      <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>scan</b></wave> button. '
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: If you feel like you have a solid suspicion, you may scan the student
      you have selected with the <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>scan</b></wave> button.
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4b2821b2272c4fd4abe2816191296e33, type: 3}
  - message: 'Upon a successful scan, the Legendary student will be revealed, and
      you will be rewarded with the opportunity to hire them as your assistant from
      the Legendary student panel.  '
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: 'Hiring each student will give you bonuses specific to their skillset,
      but it does require a small amount of <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>scholarship fund</b></wave>
      to be allocated for this purpose. So think twice before you switch your assistant,
      as you will need to expend the funds again. '
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: All three Legendary students are out there now, and may appear throughout
      any day that you work here from now on. Good luck finding them.
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
